Project Title: Project Management System

---

1. Introduction
Project Management System is a software application used to manage projects and tasks efficiently. It helps in organizing work, assigning tasks, and tracking progress.

---

2. Objective

- To create and manage projects
- To assign tasks to users
- To track task progress
- To store data using MongoDB

---

3. Technologies Used

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB

---

4. Methodology
The system is developed using REST APIs.
Data is stored in MongoDB collections:

- Projects Collection
- Tasks Collection

Operations performed:

- Insert data
- Retrieve data
- Update task status
- Manage relationships between project and tasks

---

5. Results

- Projects created successfully
- Tasks assigned and updated
- Database operations working correctly

---

6. Conclusion
The system simplifies project tracking and task management.
It improves efficiency and reduces manual errors.

---

7. Future Scope

- Add login system
- Build frontend UI
- Add notifications